def is_palindrome(s):
    # Remove spaces and punctuation, and convert to lowercase
    cleaned_s = ''.join(char.lower() for char in s if char.isalnum())
    
    # Compare the cleaned string to its reverse
    return cleaned_s == cleaned_s[::-1]
